'''Lilova Pavlovna''' (October 3, 1977) is a Russian Trucker known to be the daughter of [[Nikita Pavlovna]].
==Early life==
Born in October 3 of 1977, she spent most of his childhood in St. Petersburg, Russia (at the time known as the Soviet Union, or USSR for short), with her mother, Kristina Pavlovna, her father, [[Nikita Pavlovna]], and her brother, Mark Pavlovna. She didn't go to University.
==Career==
Lilova Pavlovna started working as a Trucker for Cash Money Transportation at 18 years old, where she still works today.

== Personal Life ==
Lilova married Kashirin Andreevna and divorced him in an unknown year, she has a daughter, Misha Andreevna.
